titleInfo.title: United States of America v. Cook
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM OPINION as to defendant Tracy A. Cook regarding Motion to Reduce Sentence, filing 153. The modifications to the United States Sentencing Guidelines do not impact his sentence as reflected in this Court's memorandum opinion of May 5, 2005 (Filing No. 138). Accordingly, defendant's motion to reduce sentence will be denied. A separate order will be entered in accordance with this opinion. Ordered by Senior Judge Lyle E. Strom. (Copy mailed/e-mailed to pro se party)(GJG)
